.SS macro FY_CPP_MAP
.INDENT 0.0
.TP
.B FY_CPP_MAP(macro, \&...) 
Apply a macro to every argument in a variadic list.
.INDENT 7.0
.TP
.B Parameters
.INDENT 7.0
.IP \(bu 2
\fBmacro\fP – Single\-argument macro to apply.
.IP \(bu 2
\fBellipsis\fP (ellipsis) – Arguments to map over.
.UNINDENT
.UNINDENT
.UNINDENT
.SS Description
.sp
Expands \fBmacro(x)\fP for each argument \fBx\fP in \fB__VA_ARGS__\fP, concatenating
all the results. The argument list must be non\-empty. Uses \fBFY_CPP_EVAL()\fP
internally, so the list length is bounded by the evaluation depth.
.sp
