.UNINDENT
.UNINDENT
.UNINDENT
.SS Description
.sp
On compilers that provide \fB__builtin_stack_restore()\fP rewinds the stack
pointer to the value captured by \fBFY_STACK_SAVE()\fP\&. On other compilers this
is a no\-op that discards \fB_x\fP\&.
