.SS macro FY_CACHELINE_ALIGN
.INDENT 0.0
.TP
.B FY_CACHELINE_ALIGN() 
Alignment attribute for cache\-line\-aligned objects.
.UNINDENT
.SS Description
.sp
Apply to a variable or struct field to ensure it starts on a cache\-line
boundary, preventing false sharing between concurrent readers/writers.
.sp
Example:
.INDENT 0.0
