.INDENT 7.0
.TP
.B Parameters
.INDENT 7.0
.IP \(bu 2
\fBp\fP (void*) – Pointer previously returned by \fBfy_align_alloc()\fP, or NULL.
.UNINDENT
.UNINDENT
.UNINDENT
.SS Description
.sp
A NULL \fBp\fP is silently ignored.
